graph TB
    subgraph "ODH Dashboard Component"
        Frontend[Frontend<br/>React + PatternFly]
        Backend[Backend<br/>Node.js + Fastify<br/>8080/TCP]
        Proxy[kube-rbac-proxy<br/>OAuth Sidecar<br/>8443/TCP]

        Frontend -->|HTTP| Backend
        Proxy -->|injects user/group headers| Backend
    end

    subgraph "Module Federation Plugins"
        GenAI[GenAI Plugin]
        ModelRegistry[Model Registry Plugin]
        MaaS[MaaS Plugin]
        KServe[KServe Plugin]
        ModelServing[Model Serving Plugin]

        Frontend -.->|loads at runtime| GenAI
        Frontend -.->|loads at runtime| ModelRegistry
        Frontend -.->|loads at runtime| MaaS
        Frontend -.->|loads at runtime| KServe
        Frontend -.->|loads at runtime| ModelServing
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources Watched"
        OdhApp[OdhApplication CR]
        OdhDoc[OdhDocument CR]
        QuickStart[OdhQuickStart CR]
        DashConfig[OdhDashboardConfig CR]
    end

    subgraph "External Access"
        User[User Browser]
        Route[OpenShift Route<br/>HTTPS/443]
    end

    User -->|HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+| Route
    Route -->|reencrypt<br/>HTTPS/8443| Proxy

    Backend -->|reads| OdhApp
    Backend -->|reads| OdhDoc
    Backend -->|reads| QuickStart
    Backend -->|reads/writes| DashConfig

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
        OAuth[OpenShift OAuth<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
        Thanos[Thanos Querier<br/>9092/TCP HTTPS]
        ModelReg[Model Registry<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS]
        Feast[Feast Registry<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS]
    end

    Backend -->|ServiceAccount Token| K8sAPI
    Proxy -->|validates token| OAuth
    Backend -->|queries metrics| Thanos
    Backend -->|API proxy| ModelReg
    Backend -->|API proxy| Feast

    subgraph "Internal ODH Integrations"
        KServeCtrl[KServe Controller]
        NotebookCtrl[Kubeflow Notebooks]
        ODHOp[ODH Operator]
        BuildSvc[OpenShift Build Service]
    end

    Backend -->|manages via K8s API| KServeCtrl
    Backend -->|manages via K8s API| NotebookCtrl
    Backend -->|reads cluster config| ODHOp
    Backend -->|triggers builds| BuildSvc

